paragraphs.body: Mindy Sterling is best known for her role as Frau Farbissina in the Austin Powers movie franchise. In 2000, her memorable portrayal earned her nominations for a Teen Choice award and a Blockbuster Entertainment Award for Favorite Supporting Actress.

paragraphs.body: Sterling has also brought her comedic talent to a number of on-camera television roles, including A.N.T. Farm, Desperate Housewives, iCarly, 2 Broke Girls, My Name is Earl, Curb Your Enthusiasm, Scrubs, King of Queens, and Reno 911!.

paragraphs.body: Sterling's voice-over credits include As Told By Ginger, The Wild Thornberrys, Kick Buttowski, The Looney Tunes Show, Scooby-Doo Mystery Incorporated, Chowder, Robot Chicken, and Justice League.
